      • setMaintenanceModeState

        public FabricHostNode.Builder setMaintenanceModeState(java.lang.String maintenanceModeState)
        Possible values are:
        • FabricHostNode.MAINTENANCE_MODE_STATE_OFF
        • FabricHostNode.MAINTENANCE_MODE_STATE_ENTERING
        • FabricHostNode.MAINTENANCE_MODE_STATE_ON
        Indicates host node's maintenance mode state. The state is ENTERING when a task to put the host in maintenance-mode is in progress. This property may be present in responses from the server, but if it is present in a request to server it will be ignored.
        Parameters:
        maintenanceModeState - New value for the property.
